  "key_dependencies": [
    "Rules → TeamRules → TeamRule (owns both nested classes)",
    "GameState → Rules (owns, reads wave config at runtime)",
    "SectorInfo ↔ GameState (write()/prepare() sync sector data ↔ state.rules)",
    "WaveSpawner → GameState.rules (reads spawns, waveTeam, dropZoneRadius, attackMode, wave)",
    "WaveSpawner → SpawnGroup (calls getSpawned(wave-1), createUnit(...))"
  ],
  "important_notes": [
    "Rules is pure config — no mutable game state, all fields are public",
    "TeamRules uses array indexed by team.id (no hashing) for efficiency",
    "GameState.set(State) fires StateChangeEvent; private state field enforces this",
    "SectorInfo.write() pushes sector-persisted values INTO state.rules (wave, waveSpacing, winWave, attackMode)",
    "SectorInfo.prepare() pulls FROM state.rules into SectorInfo before saving",
    "WaveSpawner.spawnEnemies() applies campaignRules.difficulty.enemySpawnMultiplier when isCampaign()",
    "WaveSpawner handles both ground spawns (Tile overlays) and attack-mode core spawns (wavesSpawnAtCores)",
    "WaveSpawner registered as Vars.spawner singleton",
    "GameState.hasSpawns() depends on both Rules.waves and Rules.attackMode/spawns presence"
  ],
